{"tid":1399330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大角咀禮義廉區議員拉閘笠水","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:16:43.000Z","uid":237572,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"06100dfaa4c6fc20b4a2670ddb61384cb1910a96","tid":1399330,"uid":237572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:29:48.000Z","msg":"[一手]朋友住大角咀富榮，啱啱行過見到富榮花園當區區議員，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">禮義廉鍾港武</span></span>嘅議辦，竟然拉閘！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nd037vq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnd037vq.png&h=6de27fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5nRwXk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5nRwXk.png&h=97082dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Do3dLhq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDo3dLhq.png&h=d9c89f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本係咁嘅：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGuc0Q0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGuc0Q0.png&h=e5a9036a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家忽然間想向議員求助，可以嘗試敲佢度閘，又或者喺佢個鐵閘上面直接留言。<br />\n<br />\n當然，大家都可以喺其餘時間瘋狂打俾佢求助，或者問下佢點解今日唔開門：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qTJn59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qTJn59.png&h=26c5cfd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好想瘋狂向<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鍾港武</span></span>求助呀！！！"},{"pid":"f039d334e38c69b2e9822730f0db05a062aaabdc","tid":1399330,"uid":89197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"有事就縮得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59bbfa306ff5476399f5b5c9ecfa9d2b03e9386","tid":1399330,"uid":50457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:31:35.000Z","msg":"連自己個名都遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj